name: James Martinez
description: Everyone has a good and bad side but i can only describe my good sides and things that make me who i am and leave the other for you to find out. i am simple if only you understand me to an extent, i do not worry much about my problems and i believe everyone has one. i love to make friends and socialize, am always positive about everything that matters. I love traveling, sight seeing, adventures and the sea sides. I have a small family and happy always.
